{"tid":2072199,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"移居英國前的稅務考慮 – 英國置業","createTime":"2020-06-20T12:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T13:46:16.000Z","uid":109646,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"40777870f426affc147a3e09c51a875af21a043c","tid":2072199,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:06:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>重點</strong>：如果在英國置業的目的是移居後自住，在絕大部分的情況下都應用個人名義（包括單名同聯名）買入。另外，因為按揭或貸款可以用嚟扣遺產稅，所以有幾多借幾多（另一主要原因就係宜家低息環境借錢成本低啦）。無論如何，都不應該以英國或非英國公司持有住宅物業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dm0uiFC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdm0uiFC.png&h=48b95e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本文僅討論以個人名義持有英國住宅物業以及該名個人為英國稅務居民的考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>住宅物業土地印花稅（residential Stamp Duty Land Tax）</strong><br />\n<br />\n概念如同香港買樓的印花稅（<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/stamp-duty-land-tax\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fstamp-duty-land-tax&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=94b2e6a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/stamp-duty-land-tax</a> ）。<br />\n<br />\n如置業者並非首次置業，則須基於一般稅率繳納3%的額外稅率（surcharge）。<br />\n<br />\n需要注意的是從英國稅務的角度而言，首次置業涵蓋全球的物業。因此，如果某人在香港已經持有住宅物業，並在英國購入另一住宅物業，則須繳納額外稅率。<br />\n<br />\n你可能會問英國政府如何得知置業者在海外是否持有其他物業。事實上，用常理思考都會達到同一結論：英國稅局在大部分的情況下都不會亦懶得理。同時，由於英國稅制採取自我申報機制，政府會在默認的情況下信任納稅人的申報資料。不過，稅局仍然會抽樣檢查，亦會在有人通報的情況下主動調查。誤報不但可引致額外罰款，而詐騙或故意虛報則為刑事罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eVnkqkL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVnkqkL.png&h=822b3d39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>遺產稅（inheritance tax）</strong><br />\n<br />\n前文講述過任何人，不論居籍，都須就英國財產繳付英國遺產稅（<a href=\"https://glorytohk.wordpress.com/2020/05/30/uktaxconcepts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglorytohk.wordpress.com%2F2020%2F05%2F30%2Fuktaxconcepts%2F&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=1285c1b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://glorytohk.wordpress.com/2020/05/30/uktaxconcepts/</a> ）。而假若死者離世時的居籍為英國，則須就其全球的所有資產繳納遺產稅。如死者的遺產價值高於32萬5千英鎊，則須就超額部分繳納40%的遺產稅。此外，如死者在離世前7年內向其他人作出餽贈，亦會須按照贈予年份繳納8%至40%不等的遺產稅（<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/inheritance-tax/gifts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Finheritance-tax%2Fgifts&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=fec7fc76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/inheritance-tax/gifts</a> ）。<br />\n<br />\n就持有住宅物業而言，用來置業、維護、改善物業的按揭及貸款都可用作扣除遺產稅。因此，一般的做法是在購買物業時盡可能借最多的款項以減少遺產稅風險。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>個人收入稅（income tax）</strong><br />\n<br />\n如日後有意將物業放租，租金收入的稅率則視乎於該年度的個人收入。某些費用可用作扣除須繳納稅項，如放租代理的收費。<br />\n<br />\n自住無須繳付個人收入稅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEfFqkR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEfFqkR.png&h=fac76f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>就住宅物業的資本利得稅（capital gains tax）</strong><br />\n<br />\n如日後出售物業時該物業為出售人唯一或主要的住宅物業，則可受益於私人居所稅金免除（Private Residence Relief （<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/private-residence-relief-hs283-self-assessment-helpsheet/hs283-private-residence-relief-2017--2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fpublications%2Fprivate-residence-relief-hs283-self-assessment-helpsheet%2Fhs283-private-residence-relief-2017--2&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=1afc6921\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/private-residence-relief-hs283-self-assessment-helpsheet/hs283-private-residence-relief-2017--2</a> ））而無須繳納資本利得稅。<br />\n<br />\n否則，出售物業的資本利得部分須繳納18%至28%的資本利得稅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzN4R0W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzN4R0W.png&h=fa931647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>年度住宅物業稅 (Annual Tax on Enveloped Dwellings / ATED）</strong><br />\n<br />\nATED的目標是持有英國住宅物業的英國公司或海外公司（<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/annual-tax-on-enveloped-dwellings-the-basics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fguidance%2Fannual-tax-on-enveloped-dwellings-the-basics&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=648955d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/guidance/annual-tax-on-enveloped-dwellings-the-basics</a> ）。如持有的物業價值低於50萬英鎊，亦無須繳付。如持有的物業價值高於50萬英鎊，則須每年向稅局繳付一筆稅項。<br />\n<br />\n稅局亦有列明一系列獲豁免而無需繳納ATED的情況（<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/annual-tax-on-enveloped-dwellings-reliefs-and-exemptions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fguidance%2Fannual-tax-on-enveloped-dwellings-reliefs-and-exemptions&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=7a0edff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/guidance/annual-tax-on-enveloped-dwellings-reliefs-and-exemptions</a> ），在此則不作細論了。<br />\n<br />\n如果以個人身份持有英國物業，則無須理會ATED。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ri8zuNF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRi8zuNF.png&h=804a74ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- - -<br />\n<br />\n得閒時會繼續寫唔同題目嘅文。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://glorytohk.wordpress.com/2020/06/20/ukresidentialproperty/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglorytohk.wordpress.com%2F2020%2F06%2F20%2Fukresidentialproperty%2F&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=d24966d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://glorytohk.wordpress.com/2020/06/20/ukresidentialproperty/</a>"},{"pid":"344dda8d52182d93bcd8ed459f34bda3a536d6cd","tid":2072199,"uid":53577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"剩係呢樣藍屍都唔使過去."},{"pid":"84222863d4ec50c081fcff4bcfb724efd4a2e8c4","tid":2072199,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"344dda8d52182d93bcd8ed459f34bda3a536d6cd","tid":2072199,"uid":53577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"剩係呢樣藍屍都唔使過去."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"唔知佢地換唔換BNO呢 <br />\n好似好多都照換"},{"pid":"5124aa6556d74011996c0bcc420ac11a2ce37d92","tid":2072199,"uid":272552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:43:40.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6383f9aad9037ab7225158ddc712f4fde7ae073d","tid":2072199,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:52:45.000Z","msg":"去到最好租藍屍d屋住, 剩係壞門鎖,壞熱水爐 ,燒fuse,每個月都扣幾百磅,玩殘佢哋."},{"pid":"9ffe96ae194f37312565119d126c9537a94ddaf3","tid":2072199,"uid":272552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:28:54.000Z","msg":"爸打 <br />\n如果攞BC有冇分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358ba17daa2c184ecc67a57fdea1c8417000e72a","tid":2072199,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ffe96ae194f37312565119d126c9537a94ddaf3","tid":2072199,"uid":272552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:28:54.000Z","msg":"爸打 <br />\n如果攞BC有冇分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:31:46.000Z","msg":"爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係冇任何分別嘅 都係主要睇稅務居民<br />\n不過如果英國出世又番英國住就麻煩啲"},{"pid":"3f89bbc091da8c42758bb0f1a6a567cbe700b50c","tid":2072199,"uid":34863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357ec963eaf546f867aa44b2f7048bfeb83fc772","tid":2072199,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"想知長居英國可否領取香港綜援？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4276da43e2e4ebd6e1a2b5eb4a738e8b6da5427","tid":2072199,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"即係首置stamp duty都要12%?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac9d677197129f2b969190ffb514756a786e4c7","tid":2072199,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4276da43e2e4ebd6e1a2b5eb4a738e8b6da5427","tid":2072199,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"即係首置stamp duty都要12%?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZdvVrj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZdvVrj.png&h=1a6cc07e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 最上面個總結表寫得唔清楚 呢張表會清晰啲<br />\n係高過150萬鎊嘅部分先係12%<br />\n（其實玩法同香港首置印花稅差唔多）<br />\n<br />\n例子：如果樓價根本低過12萬5千鎊，而香港/海外都冇樓，係唔洗畀stamp duty land tax添"},{"pid":"204c3312e39066ce0106d660b22b735036e21dee","tid":2072199,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"即係想買400000磅樓，而香港有樓<br />\n就要比2+3%?<br />\n如果聲稱香港冇樓，就咁2%?<br />\nthanks"},{"pid":"9506b769d5e69577939e50f513720052aee8e5cc","tid":2072199,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"357ec963eaf546f867aa44b2f7048bfeb83fc772","tid":2072199,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"想知長居英國可否領取香港綜援？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:42:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.1823.gov.hk/tc/faq/what-is-the-permissible-limit-of-absence-from-hong-kong-during-receipt-of-payment-for-cssa-recipients\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.1823.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ffaq%2Fwhat-is-the-permissible-limit-of-absence-from-hong-kong-during-receipt-of-payment-for-cssa-recipients&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=0391c199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.1823.gov.hk/tc/faq/what-is-the-permissible-limit-of-absence-from-hong-kong-during-receipt-of-payment-for-cssa-recipients</a><br />\n<br />\n就咁睇呢，每年唔可以離開香港超過60日，而60歲+就180日<br />\n<br />\n（不過社署要幾耐先發現你根本唔喺香港就當然係另一回事）"},{"pid":"9560b526474f4d0cca59a4783aa3ab02e2e600c7","tid":2072199,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9506b769d5e69577939e50f513720052aee8e5cc","tid":2072199,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"357ec963eaf546f867aa44b2f7048bfeb83fc772","tid":2072199,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"想知長居英國可否領取香港綜援？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:42:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.1823.gov.hk/tc/faq/what-is-the-permissible-limit-of-absence-from-hong-kong-during-receipt-of-payment-for-cssa-recipients\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.1823.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ffaq%2Fwhat-is-the-permissible-limit-of-absence-from-hong-kong-during-receipt-of-payment-for-cssa-recipients&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=0391c199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.1823.gov.hk/tc/faq/what-is-the-permissible-limit-of-absence-from-hong-kong-during-receipt-of-payment-for-cssa-recipients</a><br />\n<br />\n就咁睇呢，每年唔可以離開香港超過60日，而60歲+就180日<br />\n<br />\n（不過社署要幾耐先發現你根本唔喺香港就當然係另一回事）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:50:55.000Z","msg":"應該將福建計劃擴展至海外：<br />\n<br />\n於領取津貼期間，繼續在福建居留；<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/fjs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Ffjs%2F&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=9415b607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/fjs/</a>"},{"pid":"5651d850083ae43ddf34b576e8df8ec8ff419c54","tid":2072199,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"204c3312e39066ce0106d660b22b735036e21dee","tid":2072199,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"即係想買400000磅樓，而香港有樓<br />\n就要比2+3%?<br />\n如果聲稱香港冇樓，就咁2%?<br />\nthanks"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:53:18.000Z","msg":"佢唔係就咁一個固定百分比嘅稅<br />\n<br />\n如果40萬鎊嘅樓，可以係畀5千鎊（首次置業）、1萬鎊（一般稅率/非首次置業）或者2萬2鎊（香港/其他地方有樓）<br />\n<br />\n呢度有個英國稅局嘅官方SDLT計數機可以㩒下玩下 <a href=\"https://www.tax.service.gov.uk/calculate-stamp-duty-land-tax/#/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tax.service.gov.uk%2Fcalculate-stamp-duty-land-tax%2F%23%2F&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=70180e56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tax.service.gov.uk/calculate-stamp-duty-land-tax/#/</a>"},{"pid":"a4e7edd3335136175aa16f7c13735e1bfed993f7","tid":2072199,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9560b526474f4d0cca59a4783aa3ab02e2e600c7","tid":2072199,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9506b769d5e69577939e50f513720052aee8e5cc","tid":2072199,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"357ec963eaf546f867aa44b2f7048bfeb83fc772","tid":2072199,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"想知長居英國可否領取香港綜援？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:42:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.1823.gov.hk/tc/faq/what-is-the-permissible-limit-of-absence-from-hong-kong-during-receipt-of-payment-for-cssa-recipients\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.1823.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ffaq%2Fwhat-is-the-permissible-limit-of-absence-from-hong-kong-during-receipt-of-payment-for-cssa-recipients&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=0391c199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.1823.gov.hk/tc/faq/what-is-the-permissible-limit-of-absence-from-hong-kong-during-receipt-of-payment-for-cssa-recipients</a><br />\n<br />\n就咁睇呢，每年唔可以離開香港超過60日，而60歲+就180日<br />\n<br />\n（不過社署要幾耐先發現你根本唔喺香港就當然係另一回事）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:50:55.000Z","msg":"應該將福建計劃擴展至海外：<br />\n<br />\n於領取津貼期間，繼續在福建居留；<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/fjs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Ffjs%2F&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=9415b607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/fjs/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:57:50.000Z","msg":"係囉 唔明點解得福建同廣東有特別待遇 就算擴展到「臺灣省」都好啊"},{"pid":"d4ae10ba04072ee94d7c652d268228b73223837d","tid":2072199,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"204c3312e39066ce0106d660b22b735036e21dee","tid":2072199,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"即係想買400000磅樓，而香港有樓<br />\n就要比2+3%?<br />\n如果聲稱香港冇樓，就咁2%?<br />\nthanks"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:31:18.000Z","msg":"改咗小小篇文，宜家應該清晰啲。<br />\n<br />\n「計法如同香港首次置業的印花稅（<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/stamp-duty-land-tax\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fstamp-duty-land-tax&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=94b2e6a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/stamp-duty-land-tax</a> ），採用根據樓價而定的累進稅率。<br />\n<br />\n如置業者已持有另一物業，則須基於一般稅率繳納3%的額外稅率（surcharge）。<br />\n<br />\nPS 如置業者為首次置業而且物業價格不高於&pound;50萬，首&pound;30萬免稅，而其後&pound;20萬稅率為5%。如物業價格高於&pound;50萬，則全部按照一般稅率計算。」"},{"pid":"8a112c38eaf3e070165717cb2cab0a936b6b2fc4","tid":2072199,"uid":124067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:34:51.000Z","msg":"樓主點睇shared ownership？想問每個月交既租係咪等於逐步買返個權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但其實係咪搵笨？"},{"pid":"84f373a1cb5e99c58a300270d7a3e06edbec8414","tid":2072199,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a112c38eaf3e070165717cb2cab0a936b6b2fc4","tid":2072199,"uid":124067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:34:51.000Z","msg":"樓主點睇shared ownership？想問每個月交既租係咪等於逐步買返個權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但其實係咪搵笨？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"肯定唔係啦，咁咪好著數"},{"pid":"39892a9da7e116adee2c72445c841978864ee8b4","tid":2072199,"uid":124067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84f373a1cb5e99c58a300270d7a3e06edbec8414","tid":2072199,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a112c38eaf3e070165717cb2cab0a936b6b2fc4","tid":2072199,"uid":124067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:34:51.000Z","msg":"樓主點睇shared ownership？想問每個月交既租係咪等於逐步買返個權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但其實係咪搵笨？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"肯定唔係啦，咁咪好著數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"如果係咁既話買既人好傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我都係full ownership買間屋好過啦"},{"pid":"08f10a883e7a71b51271e1a99f8d5a3b7078311a","tid":2072199,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39892a9da7e116adee2c72445c841978864ee8b4","tid":2072199,"uid":124067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84f373a1cb5e99c58a300270d7a3e06edbec8414","tid":2072199,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a112c38eaf3e070165717cb2cab0a936b6b2fc4","tid":2072199,"uid":124067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:34:51.000Z","msg":"樓主點睇shared ownership？想問每個月交既租係咪等於逐步買返個權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但其實係咪搵笨？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"肯定唔係啦，咁咪好著數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"如果係咁既話買既人好傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我都係full ownership買間屋好過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:06:36.000Z","msg":"我就覺得麻麻地。<br />\n<br />\n就算日後想買埋淨番嗰啲部分，如果樓價有升，要畀嘅都多咗，所以唔覺有咩特別優惠。另外就係shared ownership全部都係leasehold唔係freehold（雖然香港啲樓都係租借地）。同埋始終喺未100%擁有層樓之前自己都仲係租客。<br />\n<br />\n如果可以嘅話，我覺得都係自己100%持有單位好好多。不過如果真係冇咁多錢又想上車嘅話，上咗半架車先都可能好過100%齋租？"},{"pid":"141a29b59019135fa81ff18dea217de0f4924c36","tid":2072199,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"Ching點睇倫敦3-4層高一大排果d樓？<br />\n定係highrise好d?<br />\n同埋睇好多盤都冇講樓齡，係咪唔重要？"},{"pid":"b1ef51f68f3431e8bbe4e4ff7ff8c1d784a6eb08","tid":2072199,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb2831461679dc83a92b54871a8fddc28d96a49","tid":2072199,"uid":109646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"141a29b59019135fa81ff18dea217de0f4924c36","tid":2072199,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"Ching點睇倫敦3-4層高一大排果d樓？<br />\n定係highrise好d?<br />\n同埋睇好多盤都冇講樓齡，係咪唔重要？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得冇乜所謂，睇位置同自己喜歡。我自己鐘意矮矮地嘅舊樓，不過純粹個人喜好。英國有啲樓啲隔音好差（不論係隔離單位定大街馬路），可以實地考察留意下。<br />\n<br />\n樓齡冇乜所謂，反而睇質素/維護。買二手樓之前要查清楚可唔可以做按揭，有啲樓啲銀行未必願意做，譬如樓下有餐廳可能有影響。同埋同香港唔同，幾百年嘅樓如果維護得OK都可以做按揭。不過舊樓都係小心漏水嗰啲啦。<br />\n<br />\n如果買樓花，小心爛尾樓（尤其倫敦以外，譬如曼城、利物浦呢啲地方）。"},{"pid":"c6145073d287045959464a765380ded4b5fc906c","tid":2072199,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T16:33:43.000Z","msg":"有朋友full pay買左倫敦同曼城樓花<br />\n有錢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢都話驚爛尾"}]}